%h1 IronJacamcar 2

%h2 Overall goals

%ul
  %li Service oriented architecture
  %li Service provider interface (SPI) for all integration points
  %li Proof of Concept for Java EE Connector Architecture 2.0
  %li Pool less container
  %li Lazy association for transacted based scenarios
  %li Serializable connection manager
  %li Fat pool lock

%p

Furthermore, IronJacamar 2 will focus on implementing the current and potential upcoming
Java EE Connector Architecture specification, and other specifications that may qualify
within this space.

%p

IronJacamar 2 should build on the feature set of IronJacamar 1.x. However, a different
implementation may be needed in order to align with the new architecture.

%p

